author: Seren Morris
title: Protests Against Lockdown in Texas, California and Seven Other States As Calls to End Stay-at-Home Orders Grow
description: Demonstrators gathered in California, Texas, Florida, Arizona, Colorado, Montana, Washington, Tennessee and Illinois to protest the stay-at-home orders.
content:
Protests against statewide lockdowns and stay-at-home orders have been taking place over the last week, with demonstrations in nine states yesterday.
